{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Can You Escape Granny's Sinister House?</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Dive into a heart-pounding horror experience where every decision could be your last.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udfda\ufe0f UNCOVER THE MYSTERIES OF A HOUSE TEEMING WITH SECRETS AND PERILS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Diverse Environments:</strong> Traverse from shadowy basements to ominous attics, each filled with secrets waiting to be discovered. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Immersive Visuals:</strong> Stunning graphics and meticulous details draw you deeper into the chilling atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/KeyPad.gif?t=1736782429\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83e\udde9 SOLVE DIVERSE PUZZLES AND OVERCOME CHALLENGES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Engaging Brain Teasers:</strong> Solve the cuckoo clock puzzle, use the metal detector to find hidden items, and test your aim in the attic shooting gallery. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Vital Tools:</strong> Locate essential items like the flare gun and phone to outsmart Granny and secure your escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/GARAGE.gif?t=1736782429\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udeaa CHOOSE YOUR ROUTE TO FREEDOM</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Flee by Car:</strong> Assemble the missing parts and speed away from terror. <br><strong>Summon Rescue:</strong> Signal for help using the flare gun and phone to bring authorities to your aid. <br><strong>Break Through the Front Door:</strong> Uncover keys and tools to make your escape through the main entrance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/CALL.gif?t=1736782429\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udfae HEART-STOPPING GAMEPLAY AGAINST A RELENTLESS FOE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Adaptive AI Enemy:</strong> Granny hears every whisper, senses your presence, and pursues you without mercy.<br><strong>Advanced Stealth Mechanics:</strong> Move silently, peek around corners, and use the environment to stay hidden. <br><strong>Unpredictable Threats:</strong> Stay vigilant\u2014danger can strike unexpectedly from anywhere.  <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/OPA.gif?t=1736782429\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udd0a IMMERSIVE AUDIO THAT AMPLIFIES THE HORROR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Atmospheric Sounds:</strong> Realistic sound effects amplify the suspense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Adaptive Soundtrack:</strong> Dynamic music intensifies during critical moments, pulling you deeper into the experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/DZINDZIN.gif?t=1736782429\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Are You Ready to Face Your Fears?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Buy now and dive into the nightmare. Your escape begins here.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc65 Join Our Community</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Connect</strong> with other players, <strong>share</strong> strategies, and <strong>get</strong> <strong>the</strong> <strong>latest</strong> <strong>news</strong> on our\u00a0<strong>Discord server or Telegram</strong>.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Escaped","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.